WEBVTT

01:37.890 --> 01:40.570
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.310 --> 01:43.580
[Episode 6]

01:45.759 --> 01:47.039
This throne—

01:49.350 --> 01:50.509
you carried me

01:51.430 --> 01:53.000
on your back,

01:54.200 --> 01:56.000
trudging through wind and snow,

01:56.350 --> 01:57.840
through dark alleys,

01:58.680 --> 02:01.400
through countless schemes,

02:01.560 --> 02:04.510
blood, and filth to seize it for me.

02:05.760 --> 02:06.840
If I lose it,

02:08.030 --> 02:10.190
there will never be anyone else

02:12.960 --> 02:14.030
to carry me

02:15.280 --> 02:17.120
and win it back again.

02:18.310 --> 02:18.960
Ding.

02:20.560 --> 02:21.690
You've already won.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.280
Relax.

02:25.430 --> 02:26.829
Get a good night's sleep.

03:07.520 --> 03:08.450
Seventh Prince.

03:08.870 --> 03:10.470
The Emperor is busy
reading memorials inside.

03:09.400 --> 03:11.100
[Young Emperor Zong Ding]

03:10.750 --> 03:12.080
He has no time to see you.

03:12.080 --> 03:13.680
You should go back first.

03:44.980 --> 03:46.350
[Young Su Taiyi]

03:47.960 --> 03:48.750
Sir.

03:49.190 --> 03:51.240
Am I Father's child?

03:52.870 --> 03:53.430
Yes.

03:54.960 --> 03:56.690
But he has many other children.

03:59.560 --> 04:00.840
But you only have

04:00.840 --> 04:03.030
me as your disciple, right?

04:04.680 --> 04:05.400
Yes.

04:06.080 --> 04:06.750
Ding.

04:07.680 --> 04:08.400
Relax.

04:09.400 --> 04:10.800
Get a good night's sleep.

05:04.510 --> 05:05.640
You're finally out.

05:06.680 --> 05:07.480
You're awake.

05:09.120 --> 05:09.720
How was it?

05:09.830 --> 05:11.270
Did you see the little Emperor?

05:11.270 --> 05:13.330
Didn't you slap him a couple of times?

05:13.800 --> 05:15.160
I don't want to talk about him.

05:15.160 --> 05:15.720
Let's go.

05:16.920 --> 05:18.120
You don't look right.

05:18.430 --> 05:20.160
Did he play tricks on you again?

05:20.600 --> 05:21.950
That's human nature.

05:22.120 --> 05:23.160
Out of a hundred emperors,

05:23.160 --> 05:24.760
a hundred would be like this.

05:25.040 --> 05:26.440
But don't let him make you

05:26.680 --> 05:27.510
think that everyone

05:27.510 --> 05:28.640
in this world is bad.

05:28.800 --> 05:30.270
We still have to

05:30.390 --> 05:31.920
change our blood and bones,

05:32.040 --> 05:32.970
become mortals,

05:33.000 --> 05:34.720
and be good people.

05:43.430 --> 05:44.830
She's such a big living human

05:44.830 --> 05:47.070
and you can't find her
after searching for so long?

05:47.070 --> 05:48.110
My Lord,

05:48.430 --> 05:50.159
that female thief is an immortal.

05:50.159 --> 05:51.290
Even if we found her,

05:51.310 --> 05:52.710
we wouldn't be her match.

05:52.950 --> 05:53.750
Do I not know

05:53.750 --> 05:54.950
that you can't beat her?

05:54.950 --> 05:56.800
It is precisely because you can't beat her

05:56.800 --> 05:58.600
that you must hurry and find her.

05:59.720 --> 06:01.240
Those people from the immortal sect

06:01.240 --> 06:02.870
pretended to cast a spell,

06:03.070 --> 06:04.800
and then there was nothing more.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.000
While they are still here,

06:06.000 --> 06:08.030
we need to find her as soon as possible.

06:08.030 --> 06:08.830
Take my token

06:09.070 --> 06:10.800
and mobilize the city guards
to set up checkpoints

06:10.800 --> 06:12.260
and search house to house.

06:12.750 --> 06:14.180
Sir, what is going on here?

06:14.180 --> 06:14.710
Exactly.

06:14.950 --> 06:16.430
Why are there checkpoints on the street?

06:16.430 --> 06:16.830
Yeah.

06:17.070 --> 06:18.630
A cultivator is causing trouble
in the city.

06:18.630 --> 06:19.390
If we can't catch her,

06:19.390 --> 06:21.120
the whole city will suffer together!

06:21.120 --> 06:22.180
I heard about that.

06:22.190 --> 06:23.560
Didn't Immortal Xin do that

06:23.560 --> 06:24.270
for Lord Lu?

06:24.750 --> 06:25.630
She doesn't kill good people.

06:25.630 --> 06:26.160
Yeah.

06:26.160 --> 06:26.870
Cut the nonsense.

06:26.870 --> 06:27.730
Pass one by one.

06:27.920 --> 06:30.520
Women must take a certificate
before leaving.

06:31.570 --> 06:32.220
Hurry up.

06:32.360 --> 06:33.000
Go, go.

06:35.070 --> 06:35.510
Pass.

06:36.070 --> 06:36.560
Go.

06:37.800 --> 06:38.330
Hurry up.

06:38.430 --> 06:39.230
Don't dawdle.

06:40.720 --> 06:41.680
That girl from the Li family
is really pretty.

06:41.680 --> 06:42.190
Yeah.

06:42.360 --> 06:43.420
You have a good eye.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.159
I am a man.

06:49.360 --> 06:50.600
The government has an order.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.950
Doors must not be closed for 3 days.

06:51.950 --> 06:53.270
All women coming in and out of the city

06:53.270 --> 06:55.159
must have a government certificate.

06:55.159 --> 06:56.360
The government has an order.

06:56.360 --> 06:58.040
Doors must not be closed for 3 days.

06:58.040 --> 06:59.270
All women coming in and out

06:59.270 --> 07:01.330
must have a government certificate.

07:01.510 --> 07:02.800
The government has an order.

07:02.800 --> 07:04.270
Doors must not be closed for 3 days.

07:04.270 --> 07:05.720
All women coming in and out of the city

07:05.720 --> 07:07.310
must have a government certificate.

07:07.310 --> 07:08.920
At the rate they're searching,

07:08.920 --> 07:10.650
they will soon find that place.

07:13.070 --> 07:15.070
How about we send her out of the city?

07:15.480 --> 07:16.680
She is badly injured.

07:16.920 --> 07:18.560
It is not convenient for her to move.

07:18.560 --> 07:20.120
What's inconvenient about it?

07:20.120 --> 07:21.270
Just carry her out.

07:21.830 --> 07:23.120
In this situation—

07:23.430 --> 07:24.560
do you think either of us

07:24.560 --> 07:26.160
should be showing our faces?

07:27.430 --> 07:28.000
True.

07:28.830 --> 07:29.630
To her,

07:30.000 --> 07:31.200
you are a dead man now.

07:31.270 --> 07:32.930
That is indeed inconvenient.

07:34.040 --> 07:35.870
Now that things
have gotten so out of hand,

07:35.870 --> 07:37.470
with Immortal Xin's temper,

07:37.740 --> 07:38.480
if she finds out

07:38.480 --> 07:40.390
you faked your death and deceived her,

07:40.390 --> 07:42.650
she will probably fight you to the death.

07:46.390 --> 07:47.520
Where are you going?

07:48.720 --> 07:49.830
Where are you going?

07:49.830 --> 07:50.960
What if they find us?

07:51.720 --> 07:52.680
Don't let them.

07:52.950 --> 07:54.880
How can I stop them from finding us?

07:55.190 --> 07:56.390
That's your problem.

07:56.560 --> 07:58.070
How did it become my problem?

07:58.070 --> 07:59.360
Isn't she your wife?

07:59.800 --> 08:00.720
How about you go to the palace,

08:00.720 --> 08:01.430
find the little Emperor,

08:01.430 --> 08:02.870
and kill that guy named Liang?

08:02.870 --> 08:03.730
When he's dead,

08:03.750 --> 08:04.510
Immortal Xin can

08:04.510 --> 08:05.570
leave the capital.

08:16.430 --> 08:17.070
Miss!

08:17.310 --> 08:19.040
My brother and I
are going to trade the hairpin

08:19.040 --> 08:20.190
for some good food.

08:20.360 --> 08:21.430
We'll be right back.

08:21.430 --> 08:22.240
Get some rest.

08:22.480 --> 08:24.480
Just leave the removed white cloth there.

08:24.480 --> 08:26.140
We'll wash it when we get back.

08:26.360 --> 08:27.290
Be careful then.

08:43.080 --> 08:44.390
The Liang Residence is at the very center

08:44.390 --> 08:45.960
of the capital's Six Streets.

08:45.960 --> 08:47.840
The left side
is close to the Imperial Guard Battalion,

08:47.840 --> 08:49.640
and the right side is a busy market.

08:49.640 --> 08:50.670
Those immortal sect disciples

08:50.670 --> 08:52.390
will definitely hide among them.

08:52.390 --> 08:53.200
If I'm not careful,

08:53.200 --> 08:54.800
I will be discovered by them.

08:55.270 --> 08:55.790
How can I

08:55.790 --> 08:56.840
quietly

08:57.010 --> 08:58.540
enter the Liang Residence?

09:34.560 --> 09:35.080
Go!

09:58.720 --> 09:59.910
Miss, we're back!

10:00.080 --> 10:00.960
Miss!

10:02.910 --> 10:03.360
Come.

10:04.080 --> 10:05.410
We have meat buns today.

10:05.600 --> 10:06.460
We bought a lot—

10:06.600 --> 10:08.870
they let us have 10 at 3 wen cheaper.

10:10.670 --> 10:12.470
I also brought medicine for you.

10:13.840 --> 10:14.640
Where did it come from?

10:14.640 --> 10:15.250
[Cures All Diseases]

10:14.730 --> 10:15.360
I picked it up.

10:15.360 --> 10:16.720
When did you pick this up?

10:16.720 --> 10:18.790
How can you give Miss
something you picked up?

10:18.790 --> 10:19.920
What if it's poison?

10:20.240 --> 10:21.170
It's not poison.

10:21.550 --> 10:24.270
It says it cures all diseases.

10:24.440 --> 10:25.840
I asked someone about it.

10:25.960 --> 10:27.290
Where did you pick it up?

10:28.150 --> 10:29.750
Just at the temple entrance.

10:32.550 --> 10:33.150
Miss,

10:34.080 --> 10:35.810
are you really going to take it?

11:26.960 --> 11:27.390
Miss!

11:27.670 --> 11:28.800
Your face is healed?

11:29.440 --> 11:30.550
What about the other injuries?

11:30.550 --> 11:31.680
Are they healed too?

11:32.750 --> 11:33.960
This elixir is rare

11:34.510 --> 11:36.170
and very helpful for healing.

11:39.840 --> 11:41.480
What are you busy with over there?

11:41.480 --> 11:42.910
Today is the third week
since Dad passed away.

11:42.910 --> 11:44.320
He'll be coming back to see us.

11:44.320 --> 11:45.240
So we bought some

11:45.240 --> 11:46.320
sacrifice offerings

11:46.320 --> 11:48.650
and we want to burn
some joss paper for him.

11:49.440 --> 11:50.300
What about you?

11:50.720 --> 11:52.380
Why do you want to get married?

11:54.200 --> 11:55.400
All my family is gone.

11:55.870 --> 11:57.200
And I'm about to die too.

11:57.320 --> 11:58.670
I've never gotten married either.

11:58.670 --> 12:00.000
I'm afraid that after I die,

12:00.000 --> 12:01.480
no one will pay respects to me.

12:01.480 --> 12:02.750
During festivals,

12:03.000 --> 12:05.460
no one will burn incense
or offerings for me.

12:30.790 --> 12:31.390
Oh, right.

12:31.600 --> 12:33.120
We also bought new clothes for Dad!

12:33.120 --> 12:34.120
Let's go get them!

12:50.270 --> 12:51.270
When I was little,

12:51.550 --> 12:52.390
a sorcerer said I had

12:52.390 --> 12:53.790
the fate of a lonely star,

12:54.510 --> 12:56.480
destined to bring death to 3 husbands.

12:56.480 --> 12:57.320
So I thought,

12:57.720 --> 12:58.980
since that's the case,

12:59.000 --> 13:00.730
I should just marry an evil man.

13:01.840 --> 13:02.900
But I didn't expect

13:03.600 --> 13:04.260
to find you.

13:05.670 --> 13:06.340
Mr. Lu,

13:07.150 --> 13:08.150
you are a good man.

13:08.750 --> 13:11.210
You shouldn't have
been harmed by villains.

13:11.300 --> 13:12.600
Was the sorcerer

13:12.600 --> 13:13.400
really right?

13:15.190 --> 13:16.370
If you hadn't met me,

13:17.000 --> 13:18.660
maybe you wouldn't have died.

13:25.790 --> 13:26.510
Mr. Lu.

13:27.510 --> 13:28.570
I have avenged you.

13:29.510 --> 13:31.000
I hope in the underworld,

13:32.030 --> 13:33.230
you can rest in peace.

13:45.360 --> 13:46.240
Lord Lu!

13:46.360 --> 13:48.760
Jiujiu and I acknowledge you
as our father!

13:48.790 --> 13:50.240
These clothes are for you,

13:50.240 --> 13:52.500
so you'll have clothes to wear in heaven!

14:52.320 --> 14:54.150
I knew were no ordinary man.

14:54.690 --> 14:57.330
But I didn't expect you to hide so well

14:58.120 --> 15:00.720
that you almost fooled me.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.030
Are you here

15:09.670 --> 15:10.630
to help me

15:11.200 --> 15:13.130
or to make things difficult for me?

15:14.790 --> 15:16.190
If you don't take action,

15:16.390 --> 15:18.720
no one will make things difficult for you.

15:22.630 --> 15:25.230
Cruel and ruthless.
You're so ungentlemanly.

15:25.670 --> 15:27.440
It’s only polite to return a favor.

15:27.440 --> 15:29.100
Don't underestimate me, Sir.

15:29.480 --> 15:30.240
I

15:30.440 --> 15:31.370
am very capable.

15:31.960 --> 15:33.290
I can eat you in one bite.

15:52.120 --> 15:53.960
Stop interfering in this matter.

15:53.960 --> 15:55.600
Leave the capital immediately,

15:55.600 --> 15:57.060
and I will spare your life.

15:58.320 --> 15:59.670
Look at what you're saying.

15:59.670 --> 16:00.800
I am not a bad person.

16:01.390 --> 16:03.510
I didn't want to make things difficult
for her either.

16:03.510 --> 16:04.910
I have no interest in her.

16:05.470 --> 16:08.220
But I am very interested in you, Sir.

16:08.790 --> 16:11.120
You are young and handsome,

16:11.360 --> 16:12.620
and powerful in magic.

16:12.990 --> 16:15.450
You don't seem like
those in orthodox sects—

16:19.970 --> 16:21.370
What is your background,

16:21.670 --> 16:23.070
and what is your purpose?

16:23.120 --> 16:25.390
You kept helping
that female cultivator.

16:25.390 --> 16:27.720
Did you fall for her?

16:31.910 --> 16:32.840
What a pity.

16:33.200 --> 16:35.890
It's unrequited love.

16:37.000 --> 16:38.840
She is avenging her husband—

16:39.150 --> 16:40.480
she is already taken.

16:41.600 --> 16:42.440
You

16:42.910 --> 16:43.870
have no chance.

16:48.720 --> 16:49.670
Don't be angry.

16:50.200 --> 16:51.750
If you don't want me to interfere,
I shan't.

16:51.750 --> 16:52.960
I'm not one of those

16:52.960 --> 16:54.820
orthodox immortal sects anyway,

16:55.000 --> 16:57.060
so I don't need to follow their rules.

16:57.360 --> 16:58.960
But let's make things clear.

16:59.270 --> 17:00.400
I'm not interfering

17:00.720 --> 17:01.550
not because

17:01.600 --> 17:03.330
I pity that female cultivator,

17:04.030 --> 17:05.880
but because of you, Sir.

17:09.200 --> 17:11.720
You are handsome and unforgettable.

17:15.240 --> 17:16.240
See you next time,

17:16.400 --> 17:17.270
young man.

17:32.790 --> 17:34.900
A bunch of people
who can't take on heavy responsibilities.

17:34.900 --> 17:36.510
Nangong Guhong is leaving too.

17:36.510 --> 17:37.960
He said his master's strings

17:37.960 --> 17:38.680
are rusted,

17:38.960 --> 17:41.270
and he has to go back
to change the strings.

17:41.270 --> 17:42.400
How absurd.

17:43.550 --> 17:45.000
He has concerns in his heart,

17:45.000 --> 17:46.510
so naturally
he is not in the mood to do things.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.570
It is human nature.

17:48.750 --> 17:50.550
Are you leaving too, Senior Jin?

17:52.030 --> 17:52.830
I still have one thing

17:52.830 --> 17:53.630
to figure out,

17:54.160 --> 17:55.490
so I won't leave for now.

17:55.590 --> 17:56.190
Forget it.

17:56.310 --> 17:57.710
I'll wait for 3 more days.

17:57.790 --> 17:59.640
If that female cultivator
still doesn't show up,

17:59.640 --> 18:00.640
I shall leave too.

18:03.850 --> 18:06.530
[Liang Residence]

18:04.440 --> 18:05.240
They all left?

18:05.510 --> 18:06.510
Master Zuo left.

18:06.980 --> 18:08.880
Master Nangong,
who is good at playing the flute,

18:08.880 --> 18:10.010
is packing his bags.

18:10.270 --> 18:11.270
Master Jiang said

18:11.350 --> 18:13.150
if there is no progress in 3 days,

18:13.350 --> 18:15.030
she will leave with Master Nangong.

18:15.030 --> 18:15.750
Do they think this capital

18:15.750 --> 18:16.550
is a place

18:16.680 --> 18:18.480
where they can come and go as they please?

18:18.480 --> 18:19.160
They boast about themselves,

18:19.160 --> 18:20.290
acting like immortals all day long.

18:20.290 --> 18:20.820
And now?

18:21.160 --> 18:22.030
They can't even find a mere

18:22.030 --> 18:23.430
Qi Refining cultivator!

18:23.480 --> 18:24.070
Useless!

18:24.200 --> 18:25.530
All of them are useless!

18:30.880 --> 18:32.110
Why are you looking at me?

18:32.110 --> 18:33.750
Are the Enchantress's whereabouts
written on my face?

18:33.750 --> 18:34.530
Go find her!

18:34.830 --> 18:36.070
Go to the County Office to get men!

18:36.070 --> 18:36.880
Go to the Court of Judicial Review!

18:36.880 --> 18:37.750
Go to the City Guard Battalion!

18:37.750 --> 18:38.510
Mobilize all the soldiers

18:38.510 --> 18:39.270
you can！

18:39.510 --> 18:41.540
Even if
you have to turn the capital upside down,

18:41.540 --> 18:42.710
find her for me!

18:43.400 --> 18:43.930
Yes, Sir.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.920
Is there really someone helping me?

20:03.030 --> 20:04.760
Fragrant sachets and pouches!

20:05.790 --> 20:07.520
Fragrant sachets and pouches!

20:08.720 --> 20:10.450
Fragrant sachets and pouches!

20:50.030 --> 20:51.360
Let's check over there.

20:57.550 --> 20:58.810
Are you looking for me?

21:00.880 --> 21:01.480
That's her!

21:01.480 --> 21:02.080
Chase her!

21:04.240 --> 21:04.790
Stop!

21:15.030 --> 21:15.550
Stop!

21:17.590 --> 21:18.200
Don't run!

21:18.590 --> 21:19.110
Stop!

21:19.160 --> 21:19.720
Don't run!

21:19.720 --> 21:21.000
-Stop running!
-Don't run!

21:21.000 --> 21:22.400
-Stop!
-Catch her! Stop!

21:22.720 --> 21:23.270
Stop!

21:23.350 --> 21:24.000
Don't run!

22:37.710 --> 22:38.440
Catch her!

22:41.400 --> 22:42.000
Catch her!

22:42.070 --> 22:43.270
Don't let her escape!

22:44.110 --> 22:45.310
Don't let her escape!

22:46.400 --> 22:47.350
An immortal cultivator!

22:47.350 --> 22:48.070
An immortal cultivator!

22:48.070 --> 22:48.790
That's so impressive.

22:48.790 --> 22:49.790
She's leaving the city.

22:49.790 --> 22:50.480
Keep chasing!

22:50.480 --> 22:51.680
-Yes, Sir!
-Yes, Sir!

23:08.030 --> 23:09.290
Senior, are you there?

23:10.030 --> 23:11.360
I have something to say.

23:17.030 --> 23:18.690
From the day I joined the sect,

23:19.160 --> 23:20.590
Master made me take a vow.

23:21.410 --> 23:22.720
He said every cultivator,

23:22.720 --> 23:24.040
upon entering the sect,

23:24.040 --> 23:25.720
must make this vow with their moral sense.

23:25.720 --> 23:26.960
I, disciple Xin Mei,

23:27.160 --> 23:29.000
take an oath here today.

23:29.310 --> 23:31.400
I voluntarily leave the mortal world

23:31.640 --> 23:33.000
and enter the immortal sect.

23:33.000 --> 23:35.730
From now on,
I will devote myself to cultivation,

23:35.750 --> 23:37.350
comprehending the Heaven's Way

23:37.350 --> 23:38.790
see things through to the end,

23:38.790 --> 23:40.310
be detached from the material world,

23:40.310 --> 23:41.960
and never use immortal magic

23:42.000 --> 23:43.400
to interfere in mortal affairs,

23:43.400 --> 23:45.060
disrupting the mortal order.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.330
If I break this oath,

23:46.400 --> 23:48.030
my moral sense will be destroyed,

23:48.030 --> 23:49.880
and I will never move past
cultivation stages.

23:49.880 --> 23:51.540
But at such critical moments,

23:51.720 --> 23:52.850
I just can't help it.

23:53.510 --> 23:54.510
Master said

23:55.310 --> 23:56.570
I am too hot-tempered.

23:56.920 --> 23:57.880
But I ask myself—

23:58.720 --> 24:00.850
it's not that I can't control my anger,

24:01.440 --> 24:04.100
but there's just something
I don't understand.

24:05.160 --> 24:07.220
With the heavenly ladder destroyed,

24:07.410 --> 24:08.650
all cultivators

24:08.680 --> 24:10.340
can almost never become gods.

24:10.490 --> 24:11.700
Then what is the point

24:11.750 --> 24:13.210
of our tough cultivation?

24:14.160 --> 24:15.690
People of the immortal sect

24:15.720 --> 24:17.240
all hold unique power,

24:17.830 --> 24:19.720
yet live in seclusion in the mountains.

24:19.720 --> 24:20.790
We can neither become gods

24:20.790 --> 24:21.650
nor be mortals.

24:22.510 --> 24:25.570
We help neither side
and have nothing to do with either.

24:26.200 --> 24:27.400
Where is the end

24:27.960 --> 24:29.290
of the Way we cultivate?

24:29.750 --> 24:30.950
And what is the origin

24:31.310 --> 24:32.970
of our so-called moral sense?

24:33.270 --> 24:33.830
Senior,

24:35.070 --> 24:36.330
if you know the answer,

24:36.830 --> 24:38.630
could you give me some guidance?

24:46.030 --> 24:47.090
It's going to rain.

24:49.510 --> 24:50.400
Anyway,

24:51.030 --> 24:53.160
thank you for meddling in my business.

24:53.160 --> 24:53.960
But in the end,

24:54.680 --> 24:56.550
it's my fault for breaking the oath

24:56.550 --> 24:57.880
and causing a disaster.

24:58.240 --> 24:59.680
Whatever the punishment,

24:59.680 --> 25:00.940
I should bear it alone.

25:01.920 --> 25:02.750
So, Senior,

25:03.400 --> 25:04.860
don't interfere anymore,

25:05.200 --> 25:06.930
so as not to be implicated by me.

25:07.440 --> 25:08.040
Thank you.

25:19.650 --> 25:22.250
♪ Once again
I see the world's cold indifference ♪

25:22.280 --> 25:25.270
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

25:25.290 --> 25:30.640
♪ Illusions and vanity blind the eyes,
how could one still care ♪

25:31.480 --> 25:33.890
♪ Once again
I see the world's cold and heat ♪

25:34.240 --> 25:37.390
♪ If no one
shares its sorrow and suffering ♪

25:37.560 --> 25:43.140
♪ The road will grow
longer and lonelier ♪

25:49.830 --> 25:50.790
No need to catch it.

25:50.790 --> 25:51.550
Let it leak.

25:52.030 --> 25:52.510
We are leaving

25:52.510 --> 25:53.510
tomorrow anyway.

25:59.790 --> 26:00.350
Where to?

26:00.920 --> 26:02.550
Are we going back to the old house?

26:02.550 --> 26:03.610
Back to Wei County.

26:03.920 --> 26:04.790
There are many soldiers outside

26:04.790 --> 26:05.720
looking for you.

26:06.680 --> 26:08.030
So we need to split up.

26:08.270 --> 26:09.670
You guys have to go first.

26:10.550 --> 26:11.480
Here, take this.

26:11.790 --> 26:13.190
Make sure to keep it safe.

26:13.310 --> 26:14.240
You are the older brother,

26:14.240 --> 26:15.770
so you will keep the silver.

26:16.440 --> 26:17.440
After you go back,

26:17.590 --> 26:18.680
go to Tianshui Lane

26:18.680 --> 26:20.480
and find an old man named Sun Yao.

26:20.590 --> 26:21.440
Tell him

26:21.440 --> 26:22.840
I sent you to look for him.

26:22.960 --> 26:24.560
He will take good care of you.

26:24.720 --> 26:25.510
This silver

26:25.510 --> 26:26.590
is enough for you to go to school

26:26.590 --> 26:27.720
and live a good life.

26:29.270 --> 26:29.730
Then...

26:30.000 --> 26:31.530
Then, when will you be back?

26:32.720 --> 26:34.350
I still have an ancestral home
in Wei County.

26:34.350 --> 26:35.410
You can live there.

26:35.680 --> 26:36.810
It's a bit run-down,

26:37.110 --> 26:39.160
but it can shelter you
from the wind and rain.

26:39.160 --> 26:40.560
Then you will have a home.

26:42.110 --> 26:43.160
But Miss,

26:43.590 --> 26:45.070
I don't want to leave you.

26:45.830 --> 26:47.680
Will you come back to see us?

26:52.510 --> 26:53.400
Rest early.

26:54.270 --> 26:56.130
You have to hit the road tomorrow.

27:26.300 --> 27:28.150
[Liang Wenjing]

27:39.720 --> 27:40.650
What is going on?

27:56.070 --> 27:56.830
This flower

27:57.240 --> 27:58.000
contains

27:58.000 --> 27:59.860
such powerful spiritual energy?

28:27.270 --> 28:29.470
I've advanced to Foundation Building.

28:35.030 --> 28:37.290
Why does this flower have such an effect?

28:37.640 --> 28:39.100
It's such a rare treasure,

28:39.110 --> 28:40.710
why would Mr. Lu give it to me?

28:41.790 --> 28:42.880
Does he know

28:42.880 --> 28:44.610
the true nature of this flower?

28:47.000 --> 28:47.400
Sir.

28:47.550 --> 28:48.510
-Stop!
-Let us out.

28:48.510 --> 28:49.200
We are in a hurry.

28:49.200 --> 28:49.910
Get in line.

28:50.190 --> 28:50.720
Hurry up!

28:52.310 --> 28:52.830
Go.

28:54.200 --> 28:54.640
Go.

29:11.000 --> 29:12.550
She's leaving just like that?

29:12.550 --> 29:13.550
People of the immortal sect

29:13.550 --> 29:15.310
are looking for her everywhere.

29:15.310 --> 29:16.510
If she doesn't leave now,

29:16.510 --> 29:18.240
it'll be hard for her to escape.

29:19.830 --> 29:21.200
It's best that she leaves.

29:21.200 --> 29:22.480
She is clear-headed.

29:24.680 --> 29:25.240
Hold up.

29:29.750 --> 29:31.610
Raise your head and lift the veil.

29:46.030 --> 29:46.510
Go, go.

29:50.110 --> 29:50.550
Go.

29:54.590 --> 29:55.190
Oh, right.

29:55.350 --> 29:57.010
Here is a letter from Su Taiyi.

29:57.110 --> 29:59.000
His Immortality Pill is almost ready.

29:59.000 --> 30:01.600
He's urging you
to return to Chongling Valley.

30:02.510 --> 30:03.000
Okay.

30:03.680 --> 30:05.140
I've indeed been delayed.

30:06.240 --> 30:06.970
You go first?

30:07.240 --> 30:08.240
I'll go find you

30:08.510 --> 30:09.270
in a few days.

30:13.440 --> 30:13.960
Why?

30:14.400 --> 30:16.260
Did you meet your old flame again?

30:17.680 --> 30:19.270
I really can't hide anything from you.

30:19.270 --> 30:20.310
Life is short.

30:20.480 --> 30:21.480
One moment of inattention,

30:21.480 --> 30:23.280
and the destined will slip away.

30:23.880 --> 30:25.350
You have so many destined ones—

30:25.350 --> 30:27.000
what's losing one or two of them to you?

30:27.000 --> 30:28.440
Whether it works out or not,

30:28.440 --> 30:29.680
I have to say goodbye.

30:29.960 --> 30:32.070
It's called finishing what I start.

30:35.440 --> 30:35.960
Okay.

30:36.750 --> 30:38.880
I'll wait for you on the official road.

31:05.960 --> 31:06.420
My Lord!

31:06.510 --> 31:07.040
How is it?

31:07.240 --> 31:08.000
Any clues?

31:08.830 --> 31:09.290
My Lord.

31:09.720 --> 31:10.270
They said

31:10.830 --> 31:11.960
when searching the city,

31:11.960 --> 31:13.750
they found
where the female cultivator was staying.

31:13.750 --> 31:14.790
Since there is a clue,

31:14.790 --> 31:17.050
tell the immortal masters immediately.

31:17.750 --> 31:18.160
Yes.

31:19.240 --> 31:20.300
Immortal Masters.

31:20.780 --> 31:22.110
At a ruined temple
in the west of the city,

31:22.110 --> 31:22.680
we found

31:22.680 --> 31:24.030
the female cultivator's clothes

31:24.030 --> 31:25.550
and a pile of firewood
that had been burning for days.

31:25.550 --> 31:26.640
The physique and time

31:26.640 --> 31:27.590
both match hers.

31:27.830 --> 31:29.440
But it seems she's gone.

31:29.880 --> 31:31.070
S-She left?

31:32.350 --> 31:33.790
There was a lot of blood on her clothes.

31:33.790 --> 31:35.200
She probably
couldn't recover from her severe injuries

31:35.200 --> 31:36.070
and found out that My Lord

31:36.070 --> 31:37.510
has been sending out troops
to capture her,

31:37.510 --> 31:38.480
so she just fled.

31:45.200 --> 31:45.790
Eat slowly.

31:45.790 --> 31:46.790
Let's go.
We still have over 10 li to go.

31:46.790 --> 31:47.270
Let's go.

31:47.270 --> 31:48.310
We should hit the road early.

31:48.310 --> 31:49.440
Let's go back early.

31:54.790 --> 31:55.920
Miss, it's ready.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.070
We can leave now.

31:57.070 --> 31:57.510
Okay.

31:58.350 --> 32:00.640
But I'll miss you.

32:02.640 --> 32:03.370
Don't worry.

32:04.000 --> 32:04.790
I'll be fine.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.410
Have a safe trip.

32:30.440 --> 32:33.150
[Liang Residence]

33:58.160 --> 33:59.420
You still dare to come?

33:59.810 --> 34:00.740
You've got guts.

34:00.880 --> 34:02.640
I haven't finished what I need to do.

34:02.640 --> 34:04.110
I haven't killed everyone I want to.

34:04.110 --> 34:04.970
How can I leave?

34:05.200 --> 34:06.260
The Second Six Line

34:06.640 --> 34:08.190
of the Hexagram Bo formation:

34:08.190 --> 34:09.590
there is no path to heaven,

34:09.590 --> 34:11.050
and no gate into the earth.

34:11.550 --> 34:13.360
With nothing and no one on your side,

34:13.360 --> 34:15.090
relying only on human harmony,

34:15.110 --> 34:15.590
Miss,

34:16.360 --> 34:18.690
how will you fight your way out
to survive?

34:20.960 --> 34:22.510
Heaven and Earth have their order;

34:22.510 --> 34:24.030
all things have their laws.

34:24.030 --> 34:25.550
You went against your moral sense

34:25.550 --> 34:26.750
and, as a cultivator,

34:27.070 --> 34:28.600
meddled in mortal affairs.

34:29.070 --> 34:30.870
You should have expected today.

34:30.880 --> 34:32.540
Using magic against mortals—

34:32.630 --> 34:34.489
you say this is bullying the weak,

34:34.630 --> 34:35.830
and it's not allowed.

34:35.920 --> 34:37.510
Then oppressing the weak with power

34:37.510 --> 34:38.800
and murdering comrades—

34:38.800 --> 34:39.960
is that not bullying the weak

34:39.960 --> 34:41.590
and throwing one's weight around?

34:41.590 --> 34:43.190
If we take this into account,

34:43.280 --> 34:46.139
they are not as daring as me
to take responsibility.

34:48.440 --> 34:50.330
Kill!

35:14.070 --> 35:15.400
To avenge your husband?

35:15.590 --> 35:17.590
You're quite a devoted soul yourself.

35:17.590 --> 35:18.320
What a pity.

35:19.030 --> 35:20.150
I am constrained by immortal sect rules

35:20.150 --> 35:21.590
and cannot help you seek revenge.

35:21.590 --> 35:22.150
However,

35:22.510 --> 35:23.550
sending you to the underworld

35:23.550 --> 35:25.210
to reunite with your husband,

35:25.400 --> 35:26.930
is something I can still do.

36:00.070 --> 36:01.000
Love

36:01.510 --> 36:02.970
hurts others and oneself.

36:03.940 --> 36:05.300
How sad and lamentable.

36:33.000 --> 36:34.530
You are the one from the inn.

37:36.630 --> 37:39.390
[Qinghong Sect, Bishui Branch]

37:48.650 --> 37:51.120
[Qinghong Sect's He Wabu]

37:55.230 --> 37:57.070
To the Phoenix God above,

37:57.590 --> 37:59.030
today we offer you

37:59.030 --> 38:00.710
fresh blood and souls,

38:01.190 --> 38:03.190
hoping for your blessing

38:03.440 --> 38:04.840
to bestow divine power

38:05.030 --> 38:07.670
and help us open the Heaven's Eye.

38:08.230 --> 38:10.360
With the blood,
we open the Heaven's Eye—

38:10.360 --> 38:11.480
rise!

38:15.480 --> 38:16.800
Phoenix God has pointed out

38:16.800 --> 38:17.930
the direction for us

38:18.110 --> 38:19.190
and found the murderer

38:19.190 --> 38:20.400
of Mr. Gui.

38:21.360 --> 38:22.800
We must thank Xunmu Vajra

38:22.800 --> 38:24.400
for bringing the Sunblock Banner

38:24.400 --> 38:26.190
so we could trace the murderer.

38:26.880 --> 38:28.920
Mr. Gui went to the capital

38:29.000 --> 38:29.840
originally to deliver goods

38:29.840 --> 38:31.040
to those big clients.

38:31.760 --> 38:33.960
He should have left
after taking the benefits,

38:33.960 --> 38:35.360
but his greed was insatiable.

38:35.360 --> 38:37.000
He meddled in other's business

38:37.000 --> 38:39.400
and brought upon himself a fatal disaster.

38:49.320 --> 38:50.780
Although the fault is his,

38:50.960 --> 38:51.670
he is, after all,

38:51.670 --> 38:53.110
the son of Xia Xuanzi.

38:53.760 --> 38:55.230
Xia Xuanzi is

38:55.670 --> 38:56.930
ruthless and vicious.

38:57.150 --> 38:58.920
He seeks revenge
for the smallest grievance.

38:58.920 --> 39:01.120
Even the Cult Master has to yield to him.

39:01.710 --> 39:02.550
Mr. Gui

39:02.710 --> 39:04.150
was a nominal elder

39:04.150 --> 39:05.410
of your Bishui Branch.

39:05.440 --> 39:07.280
Xia Xuanzi will not easily let you off

39:07.280 --> 39:08.320
or allow him

39:08.400 --> 39:09.320
to be killed

39:09.320 --> 39:10.510
at the capital.

39:11.070 --> 39:13.130
What Xunmu Vajra says is reasonable.

39:13.400 --> 39:14.190
Don't worry.

39:15.280 --> 39:16.400
I will certainly follow

39:16.400 --> 39:18.000
the guidance of Phoenix God,

39:18.150 --> 39:19.480
take that woman's life,

39:19.800 --> 39:22.130
and give Grandmaster Xia an explanation.

39:33.360 --> 39:34.150
Phoenix God

39:34.760 --> 39:36.190
has given me guidance!

39:37.190 --> 39:38.480
Phoenix God,

39:38.630 --> 39:40.230
with world-covering mighty power,

39:40.230 --> 39:41.880
is invincible!

39:42.280 --> 39:43.440
Phoenix God,

39:43.630 --> 39:45.320
with world-covering mighty power,

39:45.320 --> 39:46.960
is invincible!

39:49.230 --> 39:50.400
What are you looking for?

39:50.400 --> 39:51.920
Looking for some medicine.

39:51.920 --> 39:53.720
Jing, did you find the medicine?

39:54.400 --> 39:54.920
Yes.

39:56.550 --> 39:57.230
Make the patient's meal

39:57.230 --> 39:58.190
a bit lighter.

39:58.280 --> 39:59.320
For the other bowl of porridge,

39:59.320 --> 40:00.110
don't put salt in it.

40:00.110 --> 40:01.550
Just vegetables and meat is fine.

40:01.550 --> 40:02.950
Boil some more hot water.

40:03.110 --> 40:04.000
Okay, got it.

40:07.920 --> 40:09.030
Don't move! Let me.

40:09.710 --> 40:10.550
Let me do it.

40:12.880 --> 40:13.960
Sir, give it to me.

40:18.400 --> 40:19.800
Landlady, what are you doing?

40:19.800 --> 40:21.110
Delivering medicine.

40:21.230 --> 40:22.550
That girl is covered in injuries.

40:22.550 --> 40:23.670
If we don't apply medicine quickly,

40:23.670 --> 40:24.870
won't it leave scars?

40:25.100 --> 40:25.830
Give it to me.

40:32.110 --> 40:34.370
Sir, this medicine is from the Landlady.

40:38.960 --> 40:39.360
Here.

40:39.960 --> 40:40.560
Thank you.

40:41.760 --> 40:42.620
Thank you, Sir.

40:42.760 --> 40:43.800
You have already paid before.

40:43.800 --> 40:44.930
You are so generous.

40:50.760 --> 40:52.320
Only you have legs, only you run fast—

40:52.320 --> 40:53.520
you just have to show off, right?

40:53.520 --> 40:54.710
Landlady, it hurts!

40:54.710 --> 40:56.310
You know it hurts? Go to work!

41:00.880 --> 41:01.550
Landlady.

41:03.630 --> 41:04.320
Calm down.

41:04.840 --> 41:05.400
Have a seat.
